text: Cosmin Florin Achim (born 19 September 1995 in Drăgănești-Olt) is a Romanian footballer who plays as a defender for FC Voluntari.Adrian Iencsi a descoperit un fundaş de excepţie: "Reţineţi acest nume!" ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:People from Drăgănești-Olt Category:Romanian footballers Category:Association football defenders Category:Liga I players Category:FC Viitorul Constanța players Category:FC Voluntari players Category:Liga II players Category:ACS Viitorul Târgu Jiu players
